    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen running the installer on windows, no matter what path is used to install Neovim, it requires an administrator account. To my eyes, there is nothing about Neovim that requires an administrator account to install it to the current user.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nIn the installer, have an option to install Neovim to the current user instead of the system.",
